summary: Five TV Shows I Stopped Watching
title: Five TV Shows I Stopped Watching
body:
More often than not, a show we enjoy or love to death will lose its way and test the extent of our faithfulness to it. We can either watch it until the bitter end or let it go once we realize the magic that hooked us is gone. I have done both. How I Met Your Mother was a TV series I stuck with for pure loyalty. The struggle was real, though, and I fast forward through several of the final season episodes. The thing is, it’s much easier – and healthier, even – to just let it go. With that in mind, I compiled a list of shows to which I said goodbye before they were over, why I did it and if I would consider going back and finishing them.

KEEP READING

summary: [SPOILERS] About Qyburn, does anybody else think he’s just awesome?
title: [SPOILERS] About Qyburn, does anybody else think he’s just awesome?
body:
I’m just curious if anybody else found Qyburn to be an awesome character and had some interesting theories about him. One of my favorite things he’s done was the way he took over Varys little birds in S6 E3. I thought that was just so well done and awesome, I think he is smarter than he seems. Personally I think he has some sort of super powered quasi undead army of some type. So many people are dying around him and he seems to have permission to do any experiments he wants. That I suspect he has a lot more people turned into whatever the mountain had been. And that would be crazy but awesome.



Source: https://ift.tt/2Q12lgn
